{"id":955,"date":"2024-08-02T21:36:31","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T21:36:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=955"},"modified":"2024-08-02T21:36:31","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T21:36:31","slug":"tm083-scald","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm083-scald\/","title":{"rendered":"TM083 Scald"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM083 Scald<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found on Route 14, in the North part of the island closest to Route 6. Requires Rock Climb.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>Boiling water is shot at the foe. It may also cause a burn.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>15<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Water<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Crater Town<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm08-rock-climb\/\">Rock Climb<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>From outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon Center, start by going North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-standing-outside-of-the-crater-town-pokemon-center.jpg\" alt=\"Standing outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon  Center. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Standing outside of the Crater Town Pok\u00e9mon  Center.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go to the center of Crater Town\u2019s crater and enter Valley Cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-valley-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Entering Valley Cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering Valley Cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head West inside the cave and take the ladder to go deeper into the cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-go-deeper-inside-of-the-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to go deeper inside of the cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to go deeper inside of the cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Now, follow the cave South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-following-the-cave-south.jpg\" alt=\"Following the cave South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the cave South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll shortly have to cross two blue and white bridges, indicating you\u2019re on the right path.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-crossing-2-bridges-to-continue-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Crossing two bridges to continue going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Crossing two bridges to continue going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually come across a ladder at the very end of this cave leading you outside and to Route 6.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-exit-the-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to exit the cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to exit the cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Right after exiting the cave, walk South and cross the bridge directly in front of you.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-walking-south-after-exiting-the-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Walking South after exiting the cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking South after exiting the cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After crossing the first bridge, cross the next bridge to the West.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-crossing-the-1st-bridge-and-then-going-to-the-bridge-to-the-west.jpg\" alt=\"Crossing the first bridge and then going to the bridge to the West. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Crossing the first bridge and then going to the bridge to the West.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After crossing the second bridge, turn West and walk into the tall grass. Then follow that path going North.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/09-pokemon-unbound-walking-into-the-tall-grass-to-the-west.jpg\" alt=\"Walking into the tall grass to the West. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Walking into the tall grass to the West.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see some stairs \u2013 take them to go down to a path under the bridge you just crossed.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/10-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-path-going-east-under-the-bridge.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the path going East under the bridge. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the path going East under the bridge.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue going East even after defeating the Sun Trio and jumping off of two ledges.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/11-pokemon-unbound-jumping-off-the-ledges-and-continuing-east.jpg\" alt=\"Jumping off the ledges and continuing East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Jumping off the ledges and continuing East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see a large body of water after walking through some tall grass. When you do, use Surf to swim North and then go East when you can.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/12-pokemon-unbound-surfing-toward-the-east.jpg\" alt=\"Surfing toward the East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Surfing toward the East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll eventually land on a small island separating Route 14 from Route 6. <\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/13-pokemon-unbound-landing-on-the-small-island-to-the-east.jpg\" alt=\"Landing on the small island to the East. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Landing on the small island to the East.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go to the far North of the island to find a wall you can use Rock Climb on. The TM for Scald is on top of that wall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/14-pokemon-unbound-using-rock-climb-to-get-scald.jpg\" alt=\"Using Rock Climb to get Scald. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Rock Climb to get Scald.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":956,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-955","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/955","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/956"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=955"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=955"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}